descriptionHtml:
HD Wallpapers By Draco1122


---1,0 My first set of Pictures
---2.0 Added some more Pictures using fxaa and 16x. Let me know what you think. 


I couldn\'t help myself HD Wallpapers I just got a new graphic card and I have been loving skyrim visuals. So I took some HD screenshot of some my favorite areas. Hope you all enjoy them as wallpapers.


-Install: Unzip right click and set as wallpaper all picture are 1920x1080 .Bmp



Note: I am using Skyrim HD textures, Clear waters mod, Revamp Exterior Fog, Imaginator-Visual control device, HD 4096 water, Vurt Flora overhaul, Lush Grass, Realistic Lighting with Customization, Sexy Towns and Villages, and of coarse my mod retextures.


 
Hope you all enjoy.
